## Objective

Pico.css provides minimal, modern CSS styling for native HTML elements. Use Pico.css for base styling in Perchance projects.

---

## Usage Guidelines

-   **How to include:**

    ```html
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@picocss/pico@1.5.10/css/pico.min.css">
    ```

-   **When to use:** For consistent, modern styling of forms, buttons, tables, and all native HTML elements.
-   **Customizing:** Add project-specific CSS for overrides or enhancements.
-   **Works well with:** Shoelace, Hyperscript, and Cash DOM.

